sections.heading: notarial acts; effect.A notarial act performed prior to August 25, 1969, is not affected by sections 64-201 to 64-210
sections.text: Sections 64-201 to 64-210 provide an additional method of proving notarial acts. Nothing in sections 64-201 to 64-210 diminishes or invalidates the recognition accorded to notarial
